        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>I promise to pay <persName>Moses Austin</persName> the sum of twenty seven Dollars
and seventy five cents, in Cash on or before the <date when="1819-03-15">third Monday of
March next</date>. <date when="1819-01-07">January the 7th 1819</date>&#8212;that is in case I get seventy four
Bushels of corn from <persName>Samuel P. Brown</persName> on account of <persName>Mr Austin</persName>'s
order which he has given me for the same.</p>

<p><persName>Jn° S. Brickey</persName></p>

<p>[Moses Austin's endorsement:] Received on this Note forty five
bushels of Corn @ 37$ Cents</p>

        </div1>
